      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſch kawe arridſan\ntohs Moabiterus/ ta/ ka tee Mo-\nabiteri Dahwidam par Kalpeem\nkua Dahwanas nesdami.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dahwids kawe arridſan\nAdad-Eseru to Kehninu no Zo-\nbas/ Eemata/ kad tas nogahje\nfawu Rohbeschu iſplattiht pee\ntahs Uppeß Wrat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids atnehme teem\ntuhkſtoſchus Rattus/ un ſeptim-\ntuhkſtoſchus Jahtneekus/ un di-\nwidefmits tuhkſtoſchus Rahjinee-\nkus/ un Dahwids darrija wiſ-\nfus Rattu- (Sirgus) tifsns/\nun atlizzinaja no teem ſimts\nRattus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Sihrexi no Dar-\nmaskus nahze Adad-Eseeram\ntam Kehninain no Jobas palih-\ndseht/ bet Dahwids kawe no teem\nSihrexeem diwidefmits diwi\ntuhkſtoſchus Wihrus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids likke (Kar-\nra-Wihrus) eekſch Darnaskus\nSihrexi Semmê/ un tee Sih-\nrexi tappe Dahwidam par Kal-\npeem Dahwanas nesdami/ jo\ntas KUNGS palihdſeja Dah-\nwidu wiſſur/ kurp wiſſch gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids nehme tahs\nfelta preeſchturranas Bruz-\nnas/ kaß Adad-Esera Kalpeem\nbiſa/ un wedde tahs uhs Jeru-\nsalemi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dahwids nehme arri ſoh-\nti dauds Warra no Tibeata un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad nu Tojus tas\ndeſſch no Eematas dsirdeja\nDahwids wiſſu Karra-Sp\nAdad-Eseera ta Kehninu no\nbas bij kwis /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fuhttija wiſſch\nDehlu Adorannu pee to Kehi\nDahwidu/ pehz winna Labbi\nſchanas waizaht / un win-\npateikt/ ka tas prett Adad-\nru bij karrojis/ un winnu\nkwis/ jo Adad-Eseeram\nKarsch prett Toju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſus Selta un\nraba un Warra Rihkus /\nſwehtija tas Kehniſsch Dah-\ntam KUNGAM / lihds a\nSudrabu un Seltu / ko wi\nno wiſſeem Bagazzeem bij\nmis/ no teem Eedomiteereem\nMoabitexeem/ un no Amu-\nBehrneem / teem Wilifte-\nun no teem Amalekiteereem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Abisajus Zerujas De-\nkawe arridſan tohs Eedomit-\nSahts-Geleijā aſtonpadeti\ntuhkſtoſchus/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſch likke Ka-\nWihrus eekſch Eedoma/ un\nEedomiteri tappe Dahwi-\npar Kalpeem/ jo tas KUNG\npalihdſeja Dahwidu wiſſur/\ntas gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta waldiia Dah-\npahr wiſſu Iſraelu / un\n"
    }
